---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Trucking Insurance | RMS Insurance - We Actually Get It">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066cc 0%, #004499 100%); color: white; padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        Trucking Insurance from People Who Actually Get It
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        You're running a business from behind the wheel. Insurance shouldn't be another headache.
      </p>
      <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="btn" style="font-size: 1.25rem; padding: 16px 32px; background: white; color: #0066cc;">
        Get My Quote: 208-800-0640
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Props -->
  <section style="padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #0066cc;">Real Answers, Not Scripts</h3>
          <p>You have questions. We have answers. Not "let me check with my manager" - actual knowledge about trucking insurance from people who've done this for years.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #0066cc;">Fast When You Need It</h3>
          <p>Certificate needed at 6am before a load? We get it. Speed matters in this business.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #0066cc;">A Partner, Not Just a Vendor</h3>
          <p>We're not here to sell you a policy and disappear. We help owner-operators run their business better - insurance is just part of it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Section -->
  <section style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 3rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0066cc;">Since 2022</div>
          <div style="color: #666;">Serving Truckers</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0066cc;">2,000+</div>
          <div style="color: #666;">Truckers Helped</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0066cc;">$14M+</div>
          <div style="color: #666;">Coverage Placed</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section style="padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">How It Works</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">1</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Tell Us About Your Operation</h3>
          <p style="color: #666;">Quick call or form. We ask the right questions so you don't have to guess what we need.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">2</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Get Options That Fit</h3>
          <p style="color: #666;">We shop the same carriers everyone uses, but we explain what you're actually buying - no insurance jargon.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
          <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0066cc; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">3</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Stay Covered, Stay Moving</h3>
          <p style="color: #666;">Certs when you need them. Answers when you have questions. We're here.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2 style="text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">Common Questions</h2>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Do I really need all this coverage?</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">Some coverage is required by law (liability, cargo for certain loads). Some is smart protection. We'll tell you the difference and let you decide.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">How fast can I get a quote?</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">Most quotes same day. If you have your info ready, often within a couple hours.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Is your price lower than other agencies?</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">Honest answer: probably not. We all use the same carriers for new authorities. The price is basically the same everywhere. The difference is who picks up when you call, and whether they actually know the answer. <a href="/blog/pricing-truth">Read more about how trucking insurance pricing works.</a></p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">I just got my authority. Where do I start?</h3>
        <p style="color: #666;">Right here. <a href="/new-authorities">See our guide for new authorities.</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="padding: 4rem 0; text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ready to talk?</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #666;">Call us - we answer.</p>
      <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="btn" style="font-size: 1.5rem; padding: 20px 40px;">
        208-800-0640
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
